    Purchase options and add-ons

    Get your little ones ready for a fun and spooky celebration with this super cute Halloween coloring book! Designed especially for toddlers and kids ages 2-8, this book is filled with easy and adorable Halloween coloring pages that will keep children entertained for hours.

    From friendly ghosts, pumpkins, witches, cats, bats, and haunted houses, each illustration is simple, bold, and perfect for little hands to color. This book makes an excellent choice for families looking for Halloween gifts for kids or parents who want a fun holiday activity without screens.

    ✨ Inside this Halloween Coloring Book, You’ll Find:

    • 50 fun and easy Halloween coloring pages
    • 1 special certificate page to reward your little artist

    • Perfect for kids ages 2-8, toddlers, preschoolers, and early learners, and kids

    • Adorable characters like cats, witches, ghosts, pumpkins, bats, and haunted houses

    • Large 8.5” x 11” pages for plenty of coloring space

    • Single-sided pages to prevent bleed-through and make coloring easy

    Perfect Gift Idea for Kids:

    This Halloween coloring book is a fantastic Halloween gift, party favor, or classroom activity. It’s an engaging way to encourage creativity, improve fine motor skills, and celebrate the holiday with joy.

    Give your child a fun Halloween surprise with this Halloween Coloring Book for Kids Ages 2-8—hours of entertainment and creativity await!

    About the author

    Follow authors to get new release updates, plus improved recommendations.

    Robert Goodman

    Brief content visible, double tap to read full content.
    Full content visible, double tap to read brief content.

    Robert Goodman creates fresh and exciting ideas to support daily brain exercise, creativity, and fun—for both adults and kids. With care and imagination, he thoughtfully develops each book to surprise, engage, and inspire readers of all ages.

    From brain-boosting puzzles and interactive activity books to relaxing and playful coloring books, Robert’s work offers something for every mind and mood. Whether you’re looking to unwind, learn, or simply enjoy screen-free time, his books provide the perfect mix of entertainment and mental enrichment.

    Join Robert on a colorful and clever adventure filled with diverse puzzles, creative challenges, and fun for the whole family!

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
